            SHIPPING</button>
        <button class="p-2 w-25 btn text-light mx-5" id="addcategory">COMPETITIVE
            PRICING</button>
        <button class="p-2 w-25 btn text-light mx-5" id="addcategory">EXPERTS IN PC
